<%- include("../partials/head") %>
<%- include("../partials/header", { activePage, pageTitle }) %>

<main>
    <section class="container about-page-section">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-4 img-me">
                <img src="/images/Meganpic.jpeg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Portrait of Megan Simpson" loading="eager" width="500" height="600">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 about-text">
                <h2>About Me</h2>
                <p>Born and raised in Toronto, Ontario, I relocated to British Columbia to be closer to the mountains and the lifestyle they inspire. After living in both Vancouver and Victoria, I eventually found my home in Revelstoke, a small ski town where I now live and work.</p>
                <p>With a background in retail, inventory management, and customer experience, I currently manage Mint Day Spa. In this role, I oversee daily operations, support my team, and ensure the business runs efficiently while delivering a high-quality client experience.</p>
                <p>I am a natural problem solver with a strong curiosity about how systems function, which led me to pursue an education in software development. I am looking forward to launching my career in the industry.</p>
                <p>Outside of work, I’m most at home in the mountains. I enjoy hiking, camping, snowboarding, and spending as much time as possible outdoors. Being in nature keeps me grounded, challenges me physically, and inspires creativity. That perspective influences how I approach software development: with curiosity, resilience, and a focus on practical tools that make experiences better for real people.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="hobbies" class="row align-items-center about-lifestyle-row">
            <div class="col-md-8 about-text about-lifestyle-text">
                <p>As I continue to grow my development skills, I am excited to combine my passion for the outdoors with technology through projects that support adventure, planning, and connection with the places people care about most.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 hobbies-image about-lifestyle-image">
                <img src="/images/mountainspix.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Scenic landscape" loading="eager" width="400" height="500">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<%- include("../partials/footer") %>